    <view class="cu-avatar round lg" style="background-image:url(https://image.weilanwl.com/img/square-1.jpg);"></view>
    <view class='content'>
      <view class='text-grey'>技能服务</view>
      <view class='text-gray text-sm'>考试技巧、面试经历、手工烘焙、陪聊散心戳这里</view>
